PN,44901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,FPolicing in Northern Ireland is on a
OL,7,Fcliff edge when it comes to officer
OL,8,Fnumbers, the Police Federation has
OL,9,Fwarned.
OL,11,FThe PSNI has repeatedly said it
OL,12,Frequires 8,000 officers to fully carry
OL,13,Fout its roles but there are concerns a
OL,14,Ftarget of 7,000 by 2028 will be missed.
OL,16,FLiam Kelly, head of the Police
OL,17,FFederation, accused administrations in
OL,18,FBelfast and London of "passing the
OL,19,Fparcel of blame in a game of
OL,20,Funedifying brinkmanship".
OL,26,@zD@WOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,FMr Kelly said the PSNI is facing three
OL,7,Fyears of projected budget deficits
OL,8,Fover the next three years, with
OL,9,F"frightening numbers" from #65 million
OL,10,Fthis year, to #96 million in 2027/28,
OL,11,Fto #106 million in 2028/29.
OL,13,FHe said the books "simply cannot be
OL,14,Fbalanced", and claimed they are
OL,15,F"staring at a financial meltdown",
OL,16,Fadding: "Our political leaders must
OL,17,Fshare most of the blame for this
OL,18,Fcrisis."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@UO]uD@SOUvD@IO]wD@AOUwD@aO]xD@
OL,26,AIOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,FAddressing the Police Federation for
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's annual conference
OL,8,Fin Belfast on Wednesday, Mr Kelly also
OL,9,Fbacked a recent challenge by Chief
OL,10,FConstable Jon Boutcher to politicians
OL,11,Fto show their support for police.
OL,13,FHe said ahead of the 25th anniversary
OL,14,Fof the creation of the PSNI in
OL,15,FNovember, "the outlook has never been
OL,16,Fas bleak or filled with as much
OL,17,Fforeboding".
OL,26,@wD@KOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,FHe noted that in November 2001 there
OL,7,Fwere around 7,500 full time police
OL,8,Fofficer serving a population of around
OL,9,F1.69 million, while today there are
OL,10,F"disgracefully" 6,315 police officers
OL,11,Fserving a population of 1.93 million.
OL,13,F"When you remove student officers from
OL,14,Fthis total, the figure slides down
OL,15,Ftowards 6,000," he added.
OL,17,FMr Kelly went on to reference the many
OL,18,FStormont collapses over the last 25
OL,19,Fyears, and went on to claim that a
OL,20,F"blind eye was turned to falling
OL,21,Fpolice numbers".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]uD@AOUwD@OO]|D@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,FHe also claimed that the PSNI
OL,7,F"disgustingly remains languishing at
OL,8,Fthe back of the queue when it comes to
OL,9,Ffunding and having effective
OL,10,Fresources", as well as referencing the
OL,11,Fcurrent political failure to agree a
OL,12,Fproposed three-year budget.
OL,14,F"Devolution was meant to be a boost, a
OL,15,Fbetter way of delivering accountable
OL,16,Fgovernment," he said.
OL,18,F"In our experience, instead of being a
OL,19,Fpositive step, it has been disastrous.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]vD@AOUxD@LO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,F"We have London and Belfast passing
OL,7,Fthe parcel of blame in a game of
OL,8,Funedifying brinkmanship.
OL,10,F"We have Belfast complaining of
OL,11,Finsufficient financial resources. The
OL,12,Fpolice budget is squeezed where
OL,13,Fcontinued constrained one-year
OL,14,Ffinancial settlements are an obvious
OL,15,Fbarrier to forward-planning."
OL,17,FMr Kelly said the PSNI Recovery Plan,
OL,18,Fwhich planned to deliver an increase
OL,19,Fto 7,000 officers by April 2028, is in
OL,20,F"grave doubt".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@]O]|D@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,F"By April 2026, the end of year one of
OL,7,Fthe recovery plan, we were supposed to
OL,8,Fgrow by 150 officers so we would have
OL,9,F6,500 in service," he said.
OL,11,F"Despite the belated funding we're
OL,12,Fcurrently at 6,315 ` 35 officers less
OL,13,Fthan where the original baseline was
OL,14,Fdrawn in 2025.
OL,16,F"The next staging post in April 2027
OL,17,Fprojected we would have 6,750 officers
OL,18,Fin post. That would require a growth
OL,19,Fof 435 officers in year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,F"On average PSNI conservatively lose
OL,7,Faround 350 officers per year, so
OL,8,Frecruitment would have to be in the
OL,9,Fregion of 800 officers to just catch
OL,10,Fup.
OL,12,F"Let's be honest ` that is now simply
OL,13,Fnot going to happen. Even with the
OL,14,Fbest will in the world, the knock-on
OL,15,Feffect to get to 7,000 officers by
OL,16,FApril 2028 has effectively evaporated."
OL,18,FHe reiterated: "This is a crisis.
OL,19,FWe're not crying wolf or
OL,20,Fscaremongering", adding: "the time for
OL,21,Fintervention is right now".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@gO]zD@POU|D@OO]|D@ZOU}D@
OL,26,AZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Mr Kelly acknowledged there
OL,7,Fcould be "more from a Catholic
OL,8,Fbackground in its (PSNI) ranks".
OL,10,FBut said he said with "indifferent
OL,11,Fpolitical approach taken by some
OL,12,Fparties, combined with community
OL,13,Fopposition and a terrorist threat to
OL,14,Fthose who take the brave decision,
OL,15,Fit's little wonder there's a
OL,16,Freluctance to raise heads above the
OL,17,Fparapet and come forward".
OL,19,FHe said the reintroduction of 50-50
OL,20,Frecruitment would be a "backward step
OL,21,Fand lead to understandable resentment".
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@_O]rD@WOUyD@YO]|D@XOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,F"Engineering the figures would be a
OL,7,Flazy way of trying to fix a societal
OL,8,Fproblem," he said.
OL,10,F"From this platform today, I join the
OL,11,FChief Constable in saying bluntly that
OL,12,Fits time everyone did their bit in a
OL,13,Fmore vocal and assertive way to
OL,14,Fpromote a career in policing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,F"Those applicants from a Catholic
OL,7,Fbackground in particular have to be
OL,8,Fgiven specific reassurance from
OL,9,Fnationalist politicians and church
OL,10,Fleaders that there is no impediment or
OL,11,Fthreat to them becoming police
OL,12,Fofficers.
OL,14,F"Too often, there's a rush to
OL,15,Fcriticise, but when it comes to giving
OL,16,Fwholehearted encouragement and
OL,17,Funequivocal endorsement of a career in
OL,18,Fpolicing, quite a few usually vocal
OL,19,Fspokespeople develop a case of
OL,20,Flaryngitis.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779552674
OL,3,CPolicing on 'cliff edge' over officer
OL,4,Cnumbers
OL,6,F"Their silence is deafening."
OL,8,FHe added: "It's time for all of them
OL,9,Fto get off the fence."
OL,11,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,12,FITVX
